
meta(content='NRJohnson' property='og:title' class='var-head')
meta(content="Fantasy stories by NRJohnson." property='og:description' class='var-head')

meta(content='https://stories.nrjohnson.net/images/logo.png' property='og:image' class='var-head')

meta(content="website" property='og:type' class='var-head')
meta(content='/' property='og:url' class='var-head')
meta(name="twitter:card" content="summary" class='var-head')

<hr class='sep'>

section(class='row')
    div(class='col-12')
        h1(class='main-head-smaller') Hello! My name is 
            br(class='d-block d-lg-block')
            | N.R. Johnson.
        p Welcome to my website.
        p I am an aspiring author honing my skills by writing stories on Vocal. My first chapter (which surprisingly won a runner-up position in the Fantasy Prologue Challenge) is 
            a(href='https://vocal.media/fiction/fifty-six' target='_blank' data-tip='Read Story on Vocal') up on Vocal now
            | .
        p Fantasy and Sci-fi are what interest me, so you can expect most of my stories to be in those genres. For now, I am focusing on writing the rest of the story I started with the Vocal challenge. But I will also engage in other challenges I find interesting.
        p If you find my writing entertaining, consider signing up for updates by filling out the form at the bottom of the page. You can also send me a message by filling out the 
            a(href='/contact' class='nav-redir') Contact Me form
            | .
    
section(class='row mt-3')
    div(class='col-12')
        h2(class='main-head-smaller') My latest story:
    if story
        div(class='col-12 mb-3')
            div(class='story-card')
                div(class='row h-100 position-relative justify-content-end')
                    figure(class='col-4 m-0 p-0 story-fig')
                        img(src=story.image alt=story.title + ' cover image' class='story-image')
                    div(class='col-8 story-content')
                        h4(class='story-title')= story.title
                        hr(class='m-0 canvas')
                        div(class='story-preview')
                            | !{story.preview}
                    div(class='col-12 mb-3 mt-2')
                        div(class='row p-0')
                            div(class='col-md-6')
                                div(class='text-center mt-1')
                                    a(href='/api/about?id=' + story._id + '&route=/' class='btn w-100' data-tip='Story Details' onclick='myAlert("<h4>About ' + story.title + '</h4>' + story.about + '", null, event)') About
                            div(class='col-md-6 mt-2 mt-md-0')
                                div(class='text-center mt-1')
                                    a(href=story.url target='_blank' class='btn w-100' data-tip='Read on Vocal') Continue Reading
                                        figure(class='text-image ms-1')
